pull_request.title: Fix docs for concat file link
pull_request.body: `concat` documentation had been pointing to an invalid/outdated link. This PR corrects that to `core/perf/operators/concat` from `core/linq/observable/concat`

pull_request.title: Fix docs for flatmap unit test links
pull_request.body:
It doesn't appear that there are unit tests for `flatmapfirst.js`, `flatmaplast.js`, and `flatmapwithmaxconcurrent.js` since these are simply wrappers for constructing a new instance of `FlatMapObservable`.

I've updated these from invalid links to `None` and was thinking about later introducing some tests to verify the returned instance is the expected one.

pull_request.title: Fix docs for flatmap file links
pull_request.body: `flatMapFirst`, `flatMapLatest`, and `flatMapWithMaxConcurrent` had incorrect/outdated links to their source files. This corrects the link structure from `src/core/linkq/observable/flatmap...js` to `src/core/perf/operators/flatmap...js`
